abstracts.cdata!:
The proposed credit would finance the
            foreign exchange component of the construction of a highway
            from Amman to Zarqa, and related consultants services, the
            purchase of road maintenance equipment and consultants
            services to assist in a study of future land use and related
            transport patterns of the Amman area.
